=Description=

"Plan C is an experiment in creating forms of organisation and shared political vision which are appropriate to our present predicament. We want to reclaim collective wealth and to create and expand our collective power. From health care, education, food, water, energy, information and knowledge, the distribution of all these necessary aspects of living need to be determined democratically by the people who produce and use them."


=Status=

* We have groups in Manchester, London, Leeds, Birmingham, Teesside, Brighton, Thames Valley and Glasgow. 


